{
  "texts": [
    "This has made it more difficult for fact-checkers to verify the accuracy of information, especially online.",
    "Also, AI has increased the speed at which misinformation can spread, so AI-powered bots can spread false information on social media platforms at a much faster rate than humans can.",
    "This makes it difficult for fact-checkers to keep up with the spread of misinformation and to effectively combat it.",
    "To overcome these challenges, fact-checkers need to develop new fact-checking techniques, collaborate with AI researchers to develop more fair and unbiased AI tools.",
    "In addition, social media platforms and news organizations need to work with fact-checkers to stop the spread of misinformation."
  ]
}